{"tid":597165,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"高質高自由度江湖武俠game－漢家江湖","createTime":"2018-03-18T11:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T03:29:17.000Z","uid":157913,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ee26cc406dae9573904cf391ae52419674b57fc3","tid":597165,"uid":157913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:06:08.000Z","msg":"講明先 呢隻係一隻大陸game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸工作室做嘅獨立遊戲，回合制養成game ，如果對簡體字／大陸好反感就唔適合你了，暫時無香港代理（應該都唔會有，非食錢game)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果對簡體字／大陸game反感、好重視畫質，呢隻game未必合你心意（我都唔鐘意簡體，但好game無分國界嘅）<br />\n<br />\n但點解我會推介呢隻遊戲？我都係今日先發現到呢隻game，發覺好特別，遊戲性算好高，但呢隻game係偏向單機多啲（劇情算好好睇，起碼吸引到我唔會飛劇情），養成成份都幾重，江湖味好濃，有線上幫會同PVP功能。難得一見好玩嘅武俠game(有隻叫三少爺的劍都幾好玩，但自由度遠遠不及呢隻）<br />\n<br />\n最特別之處係自由度極大。。如果鐘意玩武林群俠傳嘅朋友應該都會鐘意呢隻game，可以自己學唔同武功／心法，每個人物都有唔同玩法，而且唔洗抽。。係靠過劇情拎人物同武學（當然你都可以抽），而且有好大嘅隨機性，你唔同嘅決定會引申到唔同嘅分支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img2.hackhome.com/img2017//5/15/17//205851568.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.hackhome.com%2Fimg2017%2F%2F5%2F15%2F17%2F%2F205851568.png&h=ad1fa0a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又可以自己加入唔同嘅門派，有主線，但可以唔跟，可以先打唔同支線，拎唔同武功同遊歷下。唔一定要衝主線。而且每個人物都有好多唔同玩法，好多套裝都有唔同效果，好似擋刀、毒效等等，好多唔同流派。<br />\n如果鐘意打裝、武俠、高自由度嘅可以一試。我自己玩咗兩日都覺得唔錯，高質game黎，非速食，但美中不足嘅係一定要大陸app store 先download到，而且只有簡體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n聯機玩法要20lv先開到，我暫時未玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但單機黎講唔錯，評論功能真係有人會評論，幾有feel。而且偏單機向，0課都玩得好開心。<br />\ndownload方法：開個大陸app store ac ，入大陸appstore 打漢家江湖<br />\n<br />\n利申非打手，大陸game無香港代理，純粹感覺隻game值得推薦先開post，有人玩可以開個幫會一齊玩（不過我都未夠lv開幫會功能）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://muzii1.168087.com/uploads/image/20170515/20170515144510_59672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmuzii1.168087.com%2Fuploads%2Fimage%2F20170515%2F20170515144510_59672.jpg&h=d7b7c267&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a831b1b6b81e267b641baac030191b5a3c63203","tid":597165,"uid":157913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:07:07.000Z","msg":"睇圖未必好吸引，但玩落係好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba35831f7d6fd587c1a541edde21fa7d56100d3f","tid":597165,"uid":157913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e0565aab61b90580b9a7aa43fe70dae467fd5c","tid":597165,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:57:31.000Z","msg":"翻去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4533d8fbc494b3e1b23979c7aaceca09c5d149","tid":597165,"uid":157913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0e0565aab61b90580b9a7aa43fe70dae467fd5c","tid":597165,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:57:31.000Z","msg":"翻去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打玩落覺得好玩 一齊研究下心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f9d0eccbe5f8f4e574c3c3b3375dc32afd2983","tid":597165,"uid":124876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:00:34.000Z","msg":"更新唔到喎 老友"},{"pid":"37a967a68ef74efcfe9a0285b11495c4b642f693","tid":597165,"uid":157913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f9d0eccbe5f8f4e574c3c3b3375dc32afd2983","tid":597165,"uid":124876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:00:34.000Z","msg":"更新唔到喎 老友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:01:25.000Z","msg":"係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我入到game"},{"pid":"409d8407671c43a1be33c23306a771